Sizing Function

In[176]:
def run_sizing(F_to_guess=10000, W_fuel_guess=10000, dW_guess=0, reheat=False, dCD0=0.0, output=True):
    if output:
        print(
            f" 0 |      |      | {round(F_to_guess):5d} | {round(W_fuel_guess):5d} | {round(dW_guess):5d} |")

    W_ramp = W_empty = 0

    # Geometry calculations
    b_ref = sqrt(AR*S_ref)
    # b_overall = 1.04 * b_ref

    Lam_le = atan(tan(Lam_c4*pi/180) + 0.25*(1-lam)/(1+lam)) * 180/pi
    c_root = 24*S_ref/(b_ref*(1+lam))
    # c_tip = lam*c_root
    # c_mac = 2/3 * c_root * (1+lam+lam**2)/(1+lam)

    S_htail = S_ref*0.24
    S_vtail = S_ref*0.265
    
    # Wetted Area calculation
    S_wet_wing = S_ref * S_wet_ratio
    S_wet_htail = S_htail * S_wet_ratio
    S_wet_vtail = S_vtail * S_wet_ratio

    r_nose = f_d / 2
    R_nose = (r_nose**2 + f_nose**2)/(2*r_nose)
    D_nose = R_nose - r_nose
    S_wet_nose_ogive = 2*pi*R_nose*(f_nose-D_nose*asin(f_nose/R_nose))/144

    S_wet_fuse_barrel = pi * f_d * (f_cylinder_len) / 144

    S_wet_fuse_cuboid = (2*f_cuboid_h+f_cuboid_w)*f_cuboid_len / 144

    S_wet_fuse = S_wet_nose_ogive + S_wet_fuse_barrel + S_wet_fuse_cuboid

    S_wet = S_wet_wing + S_wet_htail + S_wet_vtail + S_wet_fuse

    atms = ambiance.Atmosphere(0.3048*h_cruise)
    rho, delta, mu, T = 0.00194032*atms.density[0], atms.pressure[0] / \
        101325, atms.dynamic_viscosity[0] * \
        0.02088540114565743, atms.temperature[0] * 1.6828482518762586
    VTAS = M_cruise * sqrt(2402.4*T)
    KTAS = VTAS * 0.592484
    q = 1/2*rho*VTAS**2

    # Drag calculation
    Re_ft = rho*VTAS/mu
    Re = Re_ft * c_root / 12

    Cf_calc = 0.455 / (log(Re, 10)**2.58 * (1+0.144*M_cruise**2)**0.65)
    Cfe = 0.004

    CD0 = Cfe*S_wet/S_ref + dCD0
    e = 0.7
    k = 1/(pi*e*AR)

    for i in range(200):
        # Weights calculation
        W_empty = W_empty_seed + dW_guess
        W_ramp = W_empty + W_payload + W_fuel_guess

        W_ramp_max = W_empty + W_payload_max + W_fuel_guess
        # W_mzfw = W_empty + W_payload_max
        # W_mldw = 0.89 * W_ramp

        # Propulsion calculations
        W_ipps = F_to_guess / tw_ipps
        d_fan = sqrt(F_to_guess / F_to_seed) * d_fan_seed
        # d_nacelle = d_fan + 24

        # Wing weight calculation
        W_wing_structural = 19.29*(N_ult*W_ramp_max/0.05 * (1 + (tan(Lam_le*pi/180) - 2*(1-lam)/(
            AR*(1+lam)))**2) * 10**-6)**0.464 * ((1+lam)*AR)**0.7 * S_ref**0.58
        W_wing = W_wing_structural + S_ref
        

        # Delta Weights
        dW_wing = W_wing - W_wing_seed
        dW_fuse = (f_len - f_len_seed) * f_weight_len
        dW_htail = (S_htail - S_htail_seed) * htail_weight_area
        dW_vtail = (S_vtail - S_vtail_seed) * vtail_weight_area
        W_engine_to = W_ipps

        # Climb and Cruise Performance
        W_toc = W_toc_frac * W_ramp

        CL_cruise = W_toc / (q * S_ref)
        CD = CD0 + k*CL_cruise**2
        LD = CL_cruise/CD

        W_fuel_reserve = reserve_ratio * (W_ramp - W_fuel_guess)
        W_fuel_usable = W_fuel_guess - W_fuel_reserve

        range_calc = K_br * KTAS * LD / SFC * \
            log(W_ramp / (W_ramp - W_fuel_usable))

        drag_cruise = W_toc / LD
        thrust_lapse = 1.5 * delta
        F_toc_calc = (drag_cruise + W_toc*roc_toc/(VTAS*60))/(2*thrust_lapse)
        W_engine_toc = F_toc_calc/tw_ipps

        W_engine = max(W_engine_to, W_engine_toc)
        dW_engine = W_engine - (F_to_seed/tw_ipps_seed)
        dW_calc = dW_wing + dW_fuse + dW_htail + dW_vtail + dW_engine

        # Takeoff and Landing Performance
        ws = W_ramp / S_ref
        tw = F_to_guess * (1 + 0.7 * reheat) / W_ramp * n_eng

        bfl_calc = KTO*(ws / (tw * CL_max_to))

        F_to_calc = max(F_to_guess * bfl_calc/req_bfl, F_toc_calc)
        W_fuel_calc = W_fuel_guess * req_range/range_calc

        err_F_to = abs(F_to_guess - F_to_calc)/F_to_calc
        err_W_fuel = abs(W_fuel_guess - W_fuel_calc)/W_fuel_calc
        err_dW = abs(dW_guess - dW_calc)/dW_calc
        err_max = max(err_F_to, err_W_fuel, err_dW)

        F_to_guess = F_to_calc
        W_fuel_guess = W_fuel_calc
        dW_guess = dW_calc

        if output:
            print(f"{i+1:2d} | {round(range_calc):4d} | {bfl_calc:.0f} | {round(F_to_guess):5d} | {round(W_fuel_guess):5d} | {round(dW_guess):5d} | {err_max:.3e}")

        if err_max < 1e-4: # Converged
            break
        elif W_ramp > 100000:
            return np.nan, np.nan
    
    if (W_empty + W_payload_max + 5000) / S_ref > CL_max_land*req_landing_roll*mu_brake/KL:
        return np.nan, np.nan
    
    return W_ramp, W_empty

Batch Sizing and Plotting Functions

In[178]:
def gen_dimensional_diagram(AR_range, S_range, n, reheat=False, dCD0=0.0):
    M_ramp, M_empty = np.zeros((n, n)), np.zeros((n, n))

    def compute_cell(i, j, reheat=False, dCD0=0):
        global AR, S_ref
        AR = AR_range[i]
        S_ref = S_range[j]
        b_ref = sqrt(AR*S_ref)
        if b_ref > 60:
            return i, j, np.nan, np.nan

        return i, j, *run_sizing(13000, 14700, 0, reheat, dCD0, False)

    # Run in parallel over all (i, j) pairs
    results = Parallel(n_jobs=-1)(
        delayed(compute_cell)(i, j, reheat, dCD0)
        for i in range(n)
        for j in range(n)
    )

    assert results is not None
    # Fill arrays from parallel results
    # pyright: ignore[reportGeneralTypeIssues]
    for i, j, ramp_val, empty_val in results:
        M_ramp[i, j] = ramp_val
        M_empty[i, j] = empty_val

    return M_ramp, M_empty


def plot_dimensional_diagram(M_ramp, M_empty, AR_grid, S_grid, title, text_pos_left, text_pos_right):
    cmap = 'viridis'
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14,4), constrained_layout=True)

    # =========================================================
    # Helper: round to nearest 1000
    # =========================================================
    def round1000(x):
        return int(np.round(x / 1000.0) * 1000)

    # =========================================================
    # Helper to build each plot block
    # =========================================================
    def plot_block(ax, data, label, text_pos):
        valid = data[~np.isnan(data)]

        # Compute vmax from 95th percentile and round to nearest 1000
        vmax = round1000(np.percentile(valid, 95))

        # Compute vmin (rounded)
        vmin = round1000(np.nanmin(data))

        # Build contour levels every 1000
        levels = np.arange(vmin, vmax + 1000, 1000)

        # pcolormesh
        im = ax.pcolormesh(
            AR_grid, S_grid, data,
            cmap=cmap, shading='auto', vmin=vmin, vmax=vmax
        )
        fig.colorbar(im, ax=ax, label=label)

        # Contour lines
        cs = ax.contour(
            AR_grid, S_grid, data,
            colors="black", levels=levels, linewidths=0.8
        )
        ax.clabel(cs, inline=True, fontsize=8, fmt='%1.0f', colors='white')

        # Labels
        ax.set_xlabel("Aspect Ratio (AR)")
        ax.set_ylabel(r"$S_{ref}$")
        ax.set_title(label)

        # Minimum point annotation
        flat_idx = np.nanargmin(data)
        i, j = np.unravel_index(flat_idx, data.shape)
        AR_min = float(AR_grid[i, j])
        S_min = float(S_grid[i, j])
        W_min = float(data[i, j])

        ax.plot(AR_min, S_min, 'ro', markersize=8)
        ax.annotate(
            f"Min\nAR={AR_min:.2f}\nS={S_min:.0f}\nW={W_min:.0f}",
            (AR_min, S_min),
            textcoords="offset points", xytext=text_pos,
            color="white", fontsize=9, weight="bold"
        )

        return vmax, levels

    # =========================================================
    # Generate the two panels
    # =========================================================
    vmax_ramp, levels_ramp = plot_block(
        axs[0], M_ramp,  "Mission Ramp Weight", text_pos_left)
    vmax_empty, levels_empty = plot_block(
        axs[1], M_empty, "Mission Empty Weight", text_pos_right)

    plt.suptitle(title)
    plt.show()
